<p>When nature does straight lines, it does them right.</p>
<p>A flick through these pages shows some of the Highland sunsets I&#8217;ve seen in the past few years, but I&#8217;m sure the best of all might be the ones seen from this window.</p>
<p>Wherever I go in future years, this window is coming with me.</p>
